                Annual impact metrics: Review aggregated charts giving your board of
                directors clear evidence of your social footprint: 

Household status at entry;

Referral Sources;

Reason of admission and departure;

Referral sources;

Top 10 countries of origin breakdown;

Demographic pyramid using legal care age groups (0-3, 4-11, 12-17, 18-25,
                26-59, 60+) calculated against the beginning of the observed period, protecting
                historical accuracy for funding tied to minors or young adults.
